  "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/842520/extras/banner_600x60.png?t=1523103339\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Neon Void Runner</strong></h2> <br><strong>NeonVoid Runner is a infinite runner in which the player will test their reaction time in a fast virtual reality race placed in a futurist synthwave neon world . A lot of obstacles, various levels that open as you progress and of course crazy speeds await you!</strong><br><br>Player controls one of the stylized runners that can jump, slide and run. And they run faster each time player reach a checkpoint in a level. Sometimes you may encounter a blocking wall, but our characters have the power to shoot an energy ball that destroys then.<br><br><strong>How to Play:</strong><br>Up - Jump<br>Down - Slide<br>Right - Shoot energy ball.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/842520/extras/logo_600.png?t=1523103339\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES :</strong></h2><br><strong>- Synthwave neon stylized graphics</strong><br><strong>- Amazing soundtrack.</strong><br>- Supersonic speeds.<br>- Hard reaction time challenges<br>- Achievements<br>- Various levels",
